<body>
  
  <div class="ex-1">
    <h4>ex-1: Centering text with Line-Height</h4>
    
    <p>This method will work when you want to vertically center a single line of text. All we need to do is set a line-height on the element containing the text larger than its font-size.</p>
    <p>By default equal space will be given above and below the text and so the text will sit in the vertical center.</p>
    
    <div id="parent">
      <div id="child">Text here</div>
    </div>
  </div>

